      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>

  <a name="solution"></a>
  <h1>
    The Solution
  </h1>

  <p>
    The Design Sprint kicked off experiments that led us to a combination of
    general (weak behavioral knowledge) and targeted (strong behavioral
    knowledge) activation approaches, rather than a one-size-fits-all approach.
  </p>

